<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 13:25:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>波兰 Crypto MAGA 赞助商的消亡引发政治愤怒</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/demise-of-crypto-maga-sponsor-in-poland-sparks-political-furor</link><description>波兰最大的数字资产交易平台的垮台给唐纳德·特朗普在总统府的盟友带来了麻烦。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM5dz4UcSL9s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 12:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/demise-of-crypto-maga-sponsor-in-poland-sparks-political-furor</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 母公司将以 6 亿美元收购 Reap</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</link><description>加密货币交易所 Kraken 的所有者已同意向 Reap Technologies 支付 6 亿美元，Reap Technologies 是一家面向稳定币的跨境和商业支付服务提供商。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4rqC37VOMHg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 12:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</guid></item><item><title>蓝猫头鹰准备第一支基金购买二手私人信贷</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/blue-owl-preps-its-first-fund-to-buy-secondhand-private-credit</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，Blue Owl Capital 正准备推出首次信贷二级市场策略，并正在与该基金的潜在投资者进行早期谈判。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3YKD.88He1Y/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/blue-owl-preps-its-first-fund-to-buy-secondhand-private-credit</guid></item><item><title>华尔街公司发布了数十个加密货币职位——但有一个问题</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/wall-street-firms-post-dozens-of-crypto-jobs-with-a-catch</link><description>在加密货币简历中拥有华尔街的影子已经成为保持高薪就业的一种方式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijhNLZA0oZ04/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/wall-street-firms-post-dozens-of-crypto-jobs-with-a-catch</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普家族有联系的比特币矿商连续第二个季度亏损</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</link><description>美国比特币公司是特朗普家族支持的矿商，去年在最大的数字资产从历史高点暴跌之前成立，在其持有的价值下跌后，该公司连续第二个季度亏损。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itrP8ZGdUt_4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 21:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 的 Saylor 表示可能转向比特币销售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</link><description>Strategy Inc. 正在削弱其永远不会出售其持有的 670 亿美元比特币的想法。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHeGwBJsXcoQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 05:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利首次推出加密货币交易，价格低于竞争对手</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</link><description>摩根士丹利正在其 E*Trade 平台上推出加密货币交易，并讽刺竞争对手：价格更便宜。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2jiKmJEeTcI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 11:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</guid></item><item><title>拥抱人工智能，否则就会落后：加密货币公司纷纷裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</link><description>加密货币和支付公司一系列与人工智能相关的裁员给分析师和投资者带来了一个好奇的问题：如何评估人工智能部分是否真实？ &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWniLtHgFScg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 19:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</guid></item><item><title>策略通过更多炼金术在另一场比特币崩盘中幸存</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</link><description>Michael Saylor 的比特币积累公司 Strategy Inc. 通过一些新的金融工程，在另一场加密货币市场崩溃中幸存下来。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9OlmpClxkrY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 15:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</guid></item><item><title>“忧虑之墙”让散户观望最新的比特币反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</link><description>衡量市场情绪的一个关键指标几周来一直闪烁着看跌信号。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQzk9y1NgXzQ/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 以波动的市场和人工智能为由裁员 14%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</link><description>加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 将裁员约 14%，理由是需要管理动荡市场的成本和人工智能技术进步。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDpBBVhmfW64/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</guid></item></channel></rss>